{"tid":284161,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[galgame撚入] 分享下日本旅行既收獲","createTime":"2017-06-14T16:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T10:00:15.000Z","uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f86d8b0b8fed1f7b83339cfb000a86b074b2331","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"小弟上個禮拜去左日本京阪神個邊旅行<br />\n咁作為一個毒撚 去日本旅行緊係要睇毒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就係其中一日自由活動自己鼠左過日本橋掃野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大家都知日本橋有大阪秋葉原之稱 <br />\n果然皇天不負有心人 <br />\n比我揾到間做中古買取既PC game鋪<br />\n比我掃左幾隻 Gal走 (比錢個陣覺得簡直係羞恥play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n唔講咁多 去圖 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r8fveiw2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr8fveiw2&h=8b6f7a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mdul5kec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmdul5kec&h=6af39b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月社鎮社之作 <br />\n我諗年輕一代未必識佢 <br />\n但呢隻係我童年回憶<br />\n亦都係到目前為止唯一一隻推曬所有女既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢兩套野最特別係佢係初回限定版！<br />\n仲有當年本設定集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有當年PS2移值PC個隻FD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(多個綠毛可以推 仲要有H劇情 好似係呢個版本獨有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n兩套共三隻game先唔洗3000yen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉頭再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f392703455e47082352a4c56e3ff496e734360b","tid":284161,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d7c2a316f851719874aab4927a3c99a89cae27","tid":284161,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:31:25.000Z","msg":"仲有冇買其他驚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732ac76ed988ea1936754f90fc23d0a3711dbdb9","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/83ng9rjl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F83ng9rjl&h=7267091c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開箱比各位巴打睇下正版Galgame大約係點<br />\n我相信大部份玩gal既非日本人應該都好少接觸正版Gal<br />\n我呢隻係初回限定版 通常會多一隻CD<br />\n八月社就鐘意多本角色設定集"},{"pid":"58898f93420bece8c2b509f46152e637248174f0","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇買其他驚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 好眼訓 聽朝先po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e486c9b2f3eba113f12ff8cd6de3970723e835c","tid":284161,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"8月社只服穢翼"},{"pid":"b9a50862dc8a2b931c55d42207848a6cef0f0b1d","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8月社只服穢翼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依加都未捨得推呢隻<br />\n都係廢萌岩我多啲"},{"pid":"24f3c8ea87dc1fa1e3d2754172b04d60cf2b94c5","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T18:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429c6fe8ce84e9a7251b149ba15718ad4127748c","tid":284161,"uid":29011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"邊間舖？"},{"pid":"6921ec7d22a0e18a84b3627bcb7878be2af27353","tid":284161,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"樓主識睇日文？"},{"pid":"a230b663ffd83c5a9076ad652cde961163d9c17e","tid":284161,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"夜明前的菠菜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f4895310e9ef4129fc0c74db746bf295e182f1","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主識睇日文？</blockquote><br />\n學左幾年叫做識少少咁"},{"pid":"9638ff90f71359f754af591cea569e8645e592a8","tid":284161,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間舖？</blockquote><br />\n日本橋沿住行有一間樓上賣PC game好細間 <br />\n唔記得叫咩名"}]}